{"tid":1521101,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"係耶L同我入黎","createTime":"2019-08-31T05:11:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T07:06:01.000Z","uid":314131,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4fc3d4488b96047a45524169433f188a636c1b32","tid":1521101,"uid":314131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T05:11:33.000Z","msg":"一直以黎，勇武為我地打左咁多場仗<br />\n<br />\n今舖，到我地用我地嘅武器打仗<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pEkfZXw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpEkfZXw.jpg&h=3ffbdc3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n9月2號罷課集會，1點係中大烽火台一齊祈禱托住香港，之後3點半集會開始為曬所有人代禱服侍<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可能你唔係耶撚覺得我地做嘅野好無謂無用，兄弟爬山，有手足為你祈禱就乖乖地被祝福下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ronx2cr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRonx2cr.jpg&h=d847c1aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有休息站，覺得太熱太攰就乖乖地黎休息下，仲有好耐仗要打架<br />\n<br />\n#代禱者上場"},{"pid":"44e11d62f71abc3cba2ed861e1b18419182f856b","tid":1521101,"uid":314131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T05:13:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3efdaedfb5a594ad7935134b6e7f1c3f73abefc0","tid":1521101,"uid":314131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T05:13:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6a70b6fb44a0b3630c80517e176dec8f314a60ff","tid":1521101,"uid":314131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T05:14:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0c7e41dab1f38cded4fcf82109e28161a885cebd","tid":1521101,"uid":314131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T05:14:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ee9a121a1b75169d2f098cc6e944ad4f93b3e35d","tid":1521101,"uid":314131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T05:14:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0d686b53c9906649f02ac627a05bffe1cc88c876","tid":1521101,"uid":314131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"